        Our Story
      </p>
      <p class="max-w-xl mt-5 mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500">
        Born from a personal experience of loss and the desire to preserve precious memories.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <%= link_to "Start Your 1-Week Free Trial", new_user_registration_path, class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10" %>
