<!-- Story Section -->
<div class="bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="lg:text-center">
      <h2 class="text-base text-indigo-600 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">Our Journey</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-3xl leading-8 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
        When my father passed away, I was left with memories—but not his words. Not his voice. Not the full story of who he was, in his own language.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-xl text-gray-500 lg:mx-auto">
        I built VoiceThread because I wished I had something like it before he died. A way to easily sit down, press record, and let him talk. To help guide him through the story of his life, and preserve it—not just for me, but for my kids and theirs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Mission Section -->
<div class="bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
